166        }
167
168        if ($article->hasSponsorName()) {

170        }
171
172        if ($article->isSponsored()

447    private function getArticleAdUnit(Article $article): string
448    {
449        if ($article->isNoComment()) {
450            return self::ADUNIT_NOCOMMENT;
451        }
452
453        $program = '';
454        $theme = $this->getDfpTheme($article);
455
456        if (!$article->isWire()) {
457            $program = $article->getProgram()->getId();
458        }
459        $vertical = $article->getVertical();
460
461        return $vertical.'/'.$theme.'/'.$program;
462    }
463
464    protected function getDfpTheme(Article $article): ?string
465    {
466        $themeUrlSafeValue = Themes::NEWS;
467        if (!empty($article->getMainTheme()) && !empty($article->getMainTheme()->getUrlSafeValue())) {
468            $themeUrlSafeValue = $article->getMainTheme()->getUrlSafeValue();
469        }
470
471        if (!empty($article->getProgram()->getId())) { // NORMAL ARTICLE
472            $program = $this->programsApi->getProgram(['id' => $article->getProgram()->getId()]);
473            if (isset($program[0])) {
474                return $program[0]->theme;
475            }
476        }
477
478        return $themeUrlSafeValue;
479    }
